title: Sure
description: "Johnny Wilson has made a kind of name for himself in New York over the past few years. Moving from the Philadelphia scene up to New York after graduating high school, the young videographer has since done well to establish his group of friends as the unofficial face of New York City skaters. Wilson’s latest outing, simply dubbed 'Sure', is likely his best effort, surveying everywhere from Costa Rica to Los Angeles. The usual suspects make appearances in the video with some strong efforts, including Max Palmer’s creative approach to any terrain and Cyrus Bennett’s powerful, smooth moves." -Quartersnacks
